{
  "stem": "26672.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We used to eat them raw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Yeah, It was wonderful, really, really wonderful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a Rabbi Weiss, who eventually became Chief Rabbi of Zurich, who was the head of the religious, [? including ?] helpers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after, we would play football.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have a picture, a visual picture, of Rabbi Weiss standing [INAUDIBLE] standing in goal, keeping goal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there must have been 200 playing in the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was, certainly, an eye opener.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this bread, and the Marmalade, and cold milk, that was really something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember the first film we saw [INAUDIBLE] They reproduced the picture in the magazine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it came last week with that picture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was me in front, staring, eyes [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "King Henry-- I'd never seen a film before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The home I come from, it was a very-- I wouldn't say narrow-- but orthodox home, that all we were concerned about is studying, studying, studying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And apart from playing as well, I'm sure, but [INAUDIBLE] play exactly how, what, and when, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I started growing up when I was 15.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And by then, I was already a man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I had no youth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's what I regret very much-- for someone to go through life without having youth and education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had the opportunity to study.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I was frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was frightened to study.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My-- my mind would go, with so many things in mind, so many bitter things to remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was frightened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I did have a little bit of education, not very much, in Gateshead, eventually when I left Windermere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Windermere was divided up into hostels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And each town, each city, took one or two hostel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Gateshead took a hostel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they must have noticed that I was more religious.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
